-- Buffett's Berkshire to buy private auto dealer
-- By Tanya Agrawal
-- Thu Oct 02, 2014 08:51AM EDT
-- None



Oct 2 (Reuters) - Warren Buffett's Berkshire Hathaway Inc <BRKa.N> <BRKb.N> said it would buy Van Tuyl Group, the largest privately owned auto dealership group in the United States.

Berkshire did not disclose the value of the deal, but said it was expected to be completed in the first quarter of 2015. Van Tuyl will be known as Berkshire Hathaway Automotive after the acquisition and will be headquartered in Dallas, Texas, Berkshire said. [ID:nBwtYhP0a]